Class RTComponentCoupledModelDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.architectures.CoupledModelDescriptor
      • fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.plugins.devs.architectures.ComponentCoupledModelDescriptor
        • fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.plugins.devs.architectures.RTComponentCoupledModelDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentCoupledModelDescriptorI, ComponentModelDescriptorI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.architectures.ModelDescriptorI, java.io.Serializable

    public class RTComponentCoupledModelDescriptor
extends ComponentCoupledModelDescriptor
    The class RTComponentCoupledModelDescriptor implements a descriptor of a DEVS coupled models that is held by a BCM component.

    Description

    If Java allowed multiple inheritance, this class would inherit from both ComponentCoupledModelDescriptor and RTCoupledModelDescriptor. Without this possibility, the choice here is to inherit from ComponentCoupledModelDescriptor and copy the code from RTCoupledModelDescriptor. See both for more documentation applying to this class.

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2020-12-15

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant

        create a new real time component coupled model creation descriptor.

        Contract

         pre     modelClass != null || cmFactory != null
 pre     modelURI != null
 pre     submodelURIs != null && submodelURIs.size() > 1
 pre     compReflIBPURI != null
 post    CoupledModelDescriptor.checkInternalConsistency(this)
 post    ComponentCoupledModelDescriptor.checkInvariant(this)
        Parameters:
        modelClass - class defining the coupled model.
        modelURI - URI of the coupled model to be created.
        submodelURIs - URIs of the submodels of the coupled model.
        imported - map from imported event types to the submodels importing them.
        reexported - map from event types exported by submodels to exported event types exported by the coupled model.
        connections - connections between event types exported by submodels to event types imported by other submodels.
        cmFactory - coupled model factory allowing to create the coupled model or null if none.
        engineCreationMode - creation mode for the simulation engine.
        mc - model composer for this component coupled model composition.
        compReflIBPURI - URI of the coupled model holding coordinator component reflection inbound port.
        pluginClass - instantiation class of the coordination plug-in associated to the coupled model.
        pluginFactory - factory creating the instantiation class of the coordination plug-in associated to the coupled model.
